1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:04,000
chapter number four this evening, Revelation chapter number four.

2
00:00:04,000 --> 00:00:07,000
And over the last couple of Sunday evenings

3
00:00:07,000 --> 00:00:09,000
that we were in the book of Revelation,

4
00:00:09,000 --> 00:00:12,000
we dealt with verse one really,

5
00:00:12,000 --> 00:00:14,000
taking two weeks looking at that,

6
00:00:14,000 --> 00:00:16,000
dealing with the rapture and what have you.

7
00:00:16,000 --> 00:00:19,000
And this evening as we begin making progress

8
00:00:19,000 --> 00:00:21,000
through this fourth chapter,

9
00:00:21,000 --> 00:00:25,000
we find that both the context and the setting

10
00:00:25,000 --> 00:00:28,000
