11
00:00:28,000 --> 00:00:31,000
We find, I'll begin reading in verse number one

12
00:00:31,000 --> 00:00:34,000
just to get the entirety of the context.

13
00:00:34,000 --> 00:00:36,000
The Bible says, after this,

14
00:00:36,000 --> 00:00:38,000
and of course we have to understand

15
00:00:38,000 --> 00:00:40,000
what is this that he's referring to.

16
00:00:40,000 --> 00:00:43,000
And we think about the preceding text of scripture,

17
00:00:43,000 --> 00:00:45,000
chapters two and three.

18
00:00:45,000 --> 00:00:47,000
And as we look at those chapters,

19
00:00:47,000 --> 00:00:50,000
they deal with the seven letters to the churches

20
00:00:50,000 --> 00:00:54,000
and the churches throughout Asia and modern day Turkey.

21
00:00:54,000 --> 00:00:58,000
So we find that he says, after this, I looked

22
00:00:58,000 --> 00:01:02,000
and behold, a door was opened in heaven.

23
00:01:02,000 --> 00:01:04,000
The first voice, which I heard

24
00:01:04,000 --> 00:01:07,000
was as it were of a trumpet talking with me,

25
00:01:07,000 --> 00:01:10,000
