181
00:07:53,000 --> 00:07:54,000
what's going on here,

182
00:07:54,000 --> 00:07:58,000
we would say that heaven is a beautiful place.

183
00:07:58,000 --> 00:08:01,000
And we would say that for all of eternity,

184
00:08:01,000 --> 00:08:04,000
in heaven we'll be worshiping the Lord.

185
00:08:04,000 --> 00:08:07,000
By the way, he is worthy of our worship.

186
00:08:07,000 --> 00:08:08,000
He is worthy of our worship today

187
00:08:08,000 --> 00:08:11,000
and he is worthy of our worship forever.

188
00:08:11,000 --> 00:08:13,000
And we find that as we look at this text of scripture

189
00:08:13,000 --> 00:08:14,000
and begin to think about heaven,

190
00:08:14,000 --> 00:08:17,000
I've been asked, I'm sure that you have,

191
00:08:17,000 --> 00:08:18,000
