225
00:09:29,000 --> 00:09:31,000
That's why I say it's part one.

226
00:09:31,000 --> 00:09:33,000
We have the Lord's Supper that we'll be observing

227
00:09:33,000 --> 00:09:34,000
and just quite honestly,

228
00:09:34,000 --> 00:09:37,000
there's a lot in one text of scripture.

229
00:09:37,000 --> 00:09:40,000
You say, well, it's only 11 verses of scripture.

230
00:09:40,000 --> 00:09:41,000
That's true.

231
00:09:41,000 --> 00:09:43,000
But oh, how much is contained

232
00:09:43,000 --> 00:09:46,000
within these 11 verses of scripture.

233
00:09:46,000 --> 00:09:48,000
And so first I want you to notice with me

234
00:09:48,000 --> 00:09:49,000
that there is a throne.

235
00:09:49,000 --> 00:09:52,000
Notice the first thing that John says

236
00:09:52,000 --> 00:09:53,000
in verse number two, he says,

237
00:09:53,000 --> 00:09:56,000
and immediately I was in the spirit.

238
00:09:56,000 --> 00:09:58,000
And behold, notice what he says,

239
00:09:58,000 --> 00:10:00,000
a throne was made.

240
00:10:00,000 --> 00:10:04,880
was set in heaven, and one sat on the throne.

241
00:10:04,880 --> 00:10:07,340
The first thing that John begins to describe,

242
00:10:07,340 --> 00:10:09,020
and you can think about your life,

243
00:10:09,020 --> 00:10:11,260
if you have the opportunity to go somewhere,

244
00:10:11,260 --> 00:10:13,500
to see some place, and someone says,

245
00:10:13,500 --> 00:10:17,139
describe that place to me, you're gonna begin to use

246
00:10:17,139 --> 00:10:19,780
and describe with imagery and what have you

247
00:10:19,780 --> 00:10:21,260
the place that you've seen.

248
00:10:21,260 --> 00:10:23,780
And God tells us that in the text of Scripture

249
00:10:23,780 --> 00:10:26,360
that John has written these letters,

250
00:10:26,360 --> 00:10:29,079
of course, it's God speaking,

251
00:10:29,079 --> 00:10:31,360
the Lord Jesus Christ to the churches,

252
00:10:31,360 --> 00:10:34,639
and now he hears this voice and immediately

253
00:10:34,639 --> 00:10:36,759
he's in the spirit, he's in heaven,

254
00:10:36,759 --> 00:10:37,599
and what does he see?

255
00:10:37,599 --> 00:10:40,659
A throne, a throne.

256
00:10:40,659 --> 00:10:44,639
We begin to understand how this throne is described to us,

257
00:10:44,639 --> 00:10:47,520
and we'll look at the fact that the Bible says in verse two,

258
00:10:47,520 --> 00:10:49,840
and one sat on the throne,

259
00:10:49,840 --> 00:10:51,259
and we'll get to that in just a moment,

260
00:10:51,259 --> 00:10:52,759
but I want you to notice,

261
00:10:52,759 --> 00:10:54,680
just begin to think about the throne that is there.

262
00:10:54,680 --> 00:10:55,959
The Bible says in verse number three,

263
00:10:55,959 --> 00:10:58,959
and he that sat was to look upon like a jasper

264
00:10:58,959 --> 00:11:00,200
and a sardine stone,

265
00:11:00,200 --> 00:11:02,599
